data.description: Welcome to this charming home in Hobart! Conveniently located near Lake George, parks, and schools. Situated on a generously sized .25 acre lot, this property offers three bedrooms and one bathroom and nearly 1,600 sq ft. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a bright and open living room that leads to the nicely appointed eat-in kitchen. Charm and comfort combine in this perfect starter home. 2 additional bedrooms and a spacious laundry/mudroom area round out the main floor. The upper level will wow you with a great-sized bedroom/rec room, an oversized walk-in closet, and storage space. The backyard offers ample room for outdoor activities, gardening, and entertaining, and boasts a large shed that is perfect for a little extra storage. This impeccably remodeled home provides a wonderful opportunity to enjoy a story-book neighborhood close to everything! Large driveway for plenty of parking as well. Schedule your showing today!
